Carter Gibson was

21:25.610 --> 21:28.408
Carter Dunwitty until
he changed his name in 2007.

21:28.450 --> 21:30.509
Rita Dunwitty was
one of the survivors

21:30.550 --> 21:32.313
of the shooting in '87.

21:32.350 --> 21:35.410
More than that, she was married
to the shooter, Ronald Jones.

21:35.460 --> 21:37.485
BELL:
Right.

21:37.530 --> 21:38.781
So, he was Carter's father.

21:38.830 --> 21:40.354
As far as
the world knew, yes,

21:40.400 --> 21:43.028
but Carter was convinced
that Ronald Jones, the shooter,

21:43.060 --> 21:44.596
was not his father.

21:44.630 --> 21:47.337
So, he hired Fred Kirby
to run paternity tests

21:47.370 --> 21:49.338
for the four men
who were killed in '87,

21:49.370 --> 21:50.928
but none of them panned out.

21:50.970 --> 21:54.098
Sounds like
wishful thinking, right?

21:54.140 --> 21:56.574
I mean, this is a guy
who changes his name

21:56.610 --> 21:58.373
to climb out of
his family tree.

21:58.410 --> 22:00.469
Can you blame him?

22:00.520 --> 22:02.112
BELL:
Looks like Carter

22:02.150 --> 22:03.447
has some problems of his own.

22:03.490 --> 22:04.639
Disorderly conduct

22:04.690 --> 22:06.681
and resisting,
misdemeanor assault.

22:06.720 --> 22:08.051
It's a nickel-and-dime sheet,

22:08.090 --> 22:09.614
but he obviously has
a violent streak.

22:09.660 --> 22:12.720
Well, if Carter Gibson
is Ronald Jones's son,

22:12.760 --> 22:15.399
he may just be a chip
off the crazy old block.

22:15.430 --> 22:18.467
I wonder how Carter took
the news when Fred Kirby

22:18.500 --> 22:20.127
couldn't identify the dad
he was hoping for.

22:20.170 --> 22:22.638
Well, you're not the first
person to wonder that.

22:22.670 --> 22:24.729
Sherlock and the captain
took a couple of uniforms

22:24.770 --> 22:26.328
over to his house.
(phone dings)

