Building manager let us in.

22:56.640 --> 22:59.564
Got a pile of mail,
trash is ripe--

22:59.610 --> 23:02.932
doesn't look like Carter
Gibson's been home in days.

23:02.980 --> 23:06.438
Let me guess, we're thinking
he got into some kind of scrap

23:06.480 --> 23:08.869
with Fred Kirby
and Pinky Wallace right here.

23:08.920 --> 23:10.012
